<div class="article-content">
  <section>
    <p>
      We simulated a hypertension clinic in <a href="http://obvious.in/">our Bangalore office</a>, and our team played the role of nurses, doctors, and patients. <dfn>Everyone</dfn> on the team learned how hard it is to juggle the different tasks in a busy clinic and we experienced how our software fits into a healthcare worker’s job.
    </p>
  </section>
  <div class="image--wide">
    <img
      src="<%= current_page.data.cover_image_path %>"
