    <img
      src="/images/blog/how-a-simulated-clinic/stack-of-patient-ids.jpg"
      alt="A stack of patient IDs that we call \"BP Passports\""
    >
    <h4>
      A stack of patient IDs that we call "BP Passports"
    </h4>
